name: Maze (itch) (tabanopro)
description:
How To Play:

You have to figure out the exit of the maze levels.

To exit find the green circle.

Notes:

Please make sure there are less than 5 players online. Or else the game will not let you play. Also sometimes the game will not let you play because of some bugs.

This is a maze game
